==English==
=== Intransitive verb ===

# To assume a sitting position from a standing position 
#: ''Sit down!  we've got work to do.''

=== Transitive verb ===

# To coerce or force into a sitting position (from a standing position)
#: ''She sat John down and explained why she had to leave him''

